WEBVTT

00:00:00.579 --> 00:00:02.022
HR jargon makes me crazy.

00:00:02.046 --> 00:00:04.051
We have to have all these stupid acronyms

00:00:04.075 --> 00:00:08.040
that describe things that nobody
understands: OKRs and PIPs.

00:00:08.064 --> 00:00:09.699
I think we can run our businesses

00:00:09.723 --> 00:00:12.413
by just talking to each other
like regular human beings.

00:00:12.437 --> 00:00:13.880
We might actually get more done.

00:00:13.905 --> 00:00:16.688
[The Way We Work]

00:00:18.155 --> 00:00:20.791
I really always wanted to be
an HR professional,

00:00:20.815 --> 00:00:23.558
I wanted to be able to speak
the language of management.

00:00:23.582 --> 00:00:25.995
And you know what I've learned
after all this time?

00:00:26.019 --> 00:00:27.550
I don't think any of it matters.

00:00:27.574 --> 00:00:30.548
There's all kinds of things
that we call "best practices"